{
  "total_duration": 531.419,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 9.64,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象两个都会英语的人，在法国的一辆车里坐了一路，谁也不说话。不是因为他们不会说，而是因为他们都猜错了：对方应该不会英语吧？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 9.99,
      "end": 26.062,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Do you speak English?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“你会讲英语吗？”这一课不是教你学法语。它讲的是一个语言误判造成的尴尬故事：人在陌生地方，很容易先猜对方会说什么语言。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 26.412,
      "end": 46.731,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把旧背景说清楚。故事发生在法国南部，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the south of France"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，所以作者自然以为路上的人说法语。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "asked me for a lift"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是英式说法，意思是“请求搭一段车”。这是旧旅行故事里常见的场景。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 47.081,
      "end": 65.481,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但今天我们不建议小孩子模仿搭陌生人的车，也不建议随便让陌生人上车。你只需要抓住真正的笑点：在法国这个环境里，作者用法语问好，对方也用法语回了一句，于是两个其实都会英语的人，硬是沉默了一路。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 65.831,
      "end": 82.543,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这类误会今天也会发生：在机场、酒店、餐厅、博物馆、学校活动，或者线上游戏里，你以为别人听不懂你，于是少说话。直到一个简单问题出现："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Do you speak English?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "整个故事突然好笑了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 82.893,
      "end": 107.86,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一帧，故事从一个旅行经历开始："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I had an amusing experience last year."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "amusing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是轻轻好笑的，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "experience"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一件发生在你身上、后来可以讲出来的经历。作者离开法国南部的一个小村庄："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After I had left a small village in the south of France, I drove on to the next town."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 108.21,
      "end": 130.266,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二帧，路上出现一个青年人："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "On the way, a young man waved to me."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "waved"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是挥手，引起注意。作者停车后，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he asked me for a lift"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是想搭一段车。记住，这是课文里的旧旅行场景，理解短语就好，不要把它当成现代安全建议。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 130.616,
      "end": 150.111,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三帧，误会开始变尴尬。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As soon as he had got into the car, I said good morning to him in French and he replied in the same language."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "作者在法国，所以用法语问好。青年人也用同一种语言回答，这让作者更相信：对方大概只说法语。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 150.461,
      "end": 166.501,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可问题来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Apart from a few words, I do not know any French at all."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "apart from"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“除了”，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "at all"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "用在否定里加强语气。作者几乎不会法语，于是车里安静下来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 166.851,
      "end": 181.65,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四帧，安静一路以后，笑点来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Neither of us spoke during the journey."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“我们聊得少”，而是“我没有说，他也没有说”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "neither of us"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是两个人都不。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 182.0,
      "end": 198.552,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "快到镇上时，青年人突然慢慢问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Do you speak English?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一句一出来，前面的沉默全变好笑了。作者很快知道："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he was English himself"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。原来两个人本来就可以用英语聊天。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 198.902,
      "end": 202.262,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇故事的笑点在哪里？是作者不会法语吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 202.612,
      "end": 209.36,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好像不是。不会法语只是让他沉默，真正好笑的是他们两个都会英语。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 209.71,
      "end": 221.75,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。法国这个环境让作者先做了一个假设：这个青年人可能说法语。青年人也用法语回了一句，于是这个假设看起来更像真的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 222.1,
      "end": 224.814,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那青年人为什么也不说话？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 225.164,
      "end": 238.804,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文没有直接解释，但我们能感觉到他也许同样在等，也许也以为作者不想说英语，或者不知道该用什么语言开口。两个人都很礼貌，却都没问关键问题。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 239.154,
      "end": 243.224,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Neither of us spoke"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "要怎么理解？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 243.574,
      "end": 254.966,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "它强调两边都没有开口："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "neither"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“两个都不”。不是只有作者安静，也不是只有青年人安静，而是整个旅程都被这个错误假设按了静音键。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 255.316,
      "end": 260.643,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以最后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Do you speak English?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "像一个开关。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 260.993,
      "end": 274.425,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很准确。这个简单问题一问出来，误会就解开了。你也可以记住一个现代版本：如果不确定别人会不会英语，不要自己闷着猜，可以礼貌地问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Do you speak English?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
